&lt;p&gt;Scale is building AI for the world’s most important decisions. From the front lines of national defense to the core of global enterprise, we provide the data engine and agentic infrastructure that powers the next generation of American and allied interests.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Defense Deployment Strategist, you will be responsible for bridging the gap between cutting-edge AI research and mission-critical production. You will lead the charge in deploying Agentic AI — autonomous, reasoning systems — into the heart of defense workflows, ensuring that our nation&#39;s most complex decisions are supported by the world’s best technology.&lt;/p&gt;
